Package org.neo4j.kernel.api.index

Interface NonUniqueIndexSampler

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultNonUniqueIndexSampler, FullScanNonUniqueIndexSampler, NonUniqueIndexSampler.Adapter
    public interface NonUniqueIndexSampler
    Builds index sample. It's implementation specific how sample will be build: using index directly or based on samples provided through various include/exclude calls
